Class StateValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • param.StateValues

  • public final class StateValues
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to assign a value to each state of a model. Used by RegionValues.
    Author:
    Ernst Moritz Hahn (University of Oxford)
    See Also:
    RegionValues
